          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1684230212459-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong>, <strong>sliced cucumber</strong> and <strong>chopped coriander</strong> to a bowl with the juice of the <strong>remaining lime</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside for later – this is your <strong>cucumber & shallot salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
