    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>tofu </strong>and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Grate the <strong>tofu</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated tofu </strong>to a large bowl with the <strong>remaining soy sauce</strong>,<strong> tamarind paste</strong>, <strong>cornflour</strong>,<strong> </strong>2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong>,<strong> </strong>50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]<strong> </span>cold water </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tofu fritter batter</strong></p>",
