      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, spread a dollop of <strong>satay sauce</strong> on each <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>ciabatta base</strong>, then stack them up with the <strong>tofu fritters </strong>and some of the <strong>cucumber & shallot salad </strong>– these are your <strong>tofu fritter burgers</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>tofu fritter burgers </strong>with the <strong>chips </strong>and any <strong>remaining cucumber & shallot salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
